public record FirstLevelDivision(int divisionId, String divisionName, Timestamp createDate, String createdBy, Timestamp lastUpdate, String lastUpdateBy, Country country) extends Record
A data carrier class that contains database CRUD operations as static methods for the first_level_divisions table. A row returned from the table is packaged as a FirstLevelDivision data-transfer-like object.
